	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: A question about the MMC5 &amp; NES original PCM.</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />FCEUX is running a bandlimited sound synthesizer, with things like filters and DC cancellation, so its output isn't going to match the input identically.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
